of Valtistm 
EXTRAORDINARY 
PUBLISHED BY AUTHORITY 
ISLAMABAD, WEDNESDAY, FEBRUARY 3,2016 
PART II 
Statutory Notifications (S. II. 0.) 
GOVERNMENT OF PAKISTAN 
REVENUE DIVISION 
(Federal Board of Revenue) 
NOTIFICATION 
Islamabad, the 1st February, 2016 
(CUSTOMS) 
S.R.O. 79 (1)12016.- In exercise of the powers conferred by section 219 
of the Customs Act, 1969 (IV of 1969), the Federal Board of Revenue is pleased 
to direct that the following further amendments shall be made in the Customs 
Rules, 2001, namely:- 
In the aforesaid Rules, in Chapter XXVI,- 
(a) 	the existing rules 592, 593, 594, 595, 596, 597, 598, 599, 600, 601, 
602, 603, 604, 605, 606, 607 and 608, shall be re-numbered. as 653, 
654, 655, 656, 657, 658, 659, 660, 661, 662, 663, 664, 665, 666, 
667, 668, 669 respectively; 
(359) 
2234 (2016)/Ex. Gaz.] 	Price: Rs. 2.00
